text: Leeroy Takunda Maguraushe (born 11 January 1996) is a Zimbabwean-born-English footballer who plays as a midfielder, most recently for San Antonio FC in the USL Championship. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at UNC Greensboro Athletics Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Luton Town F.C. players Category:UNC Greensboro Spartans men's soccer players Category:Seattle Sounders FC U-23 players Category:San Antonio FC players Category:USL Championship players Category:USL League Two players Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Zimbabwean expatriate footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Sportspeople from Bulawayo
